        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Bostryx rudisculptus (Parodiz, 1956) (holotype MACN-In 380). (A) Shell in ventral, dorsal and lateral view; (B) detail of beginning of protoconch; (C) detail of second whorl of protoconch; (D) detail of protoconch’s sculpture between the first and second whorl; (E) detail of protoconch’s sculpture between the second and third whorl." ;
